creator: NTrust Infotech
descriptionHtml: NTrust is the global industry leader specializing in delivery of technology-enabled services for the CRE industry. Established in 2003 by CRE industry specialists, NTrust has over 900 employees worldwide and has completed over 950,000 lease abstracts from 40 languages and 106 countries. Our clients include global REITs, owner/developers, service providers and occupiers.
descriptionShort: NTrust provides the best CRE software platforms and technology-enabled services
title: REAP

creator: NTrust Infotech
descriptionHtml:
REAP+ is a full-featured software for office and retail occupiers with multi-currency capabilities, and can handle both real estate and equipment leases. Get all these benefits with no-hassle pricing and low implementation cost. And REAP+ is fully FAS and IFRS compliant and provides the full range of ASC 842 reports

1. Designed to be comprehensive and easy to use, REAP+ provides a flexible and easy to maintain platform for retail, industrial, distribution and office occupiers.

2. Report Writing without IT – write and share reports using Report Builder’s simple and easy-to-use interface.

3. FAS and IFRS Compliance with full ASC 842 Reporting capabilities.

4.Security – with flexible role-based user security, you can control what each user sees and has access to.
descriptionShort: Lease Management Software with full ASC 842 and IFRS functionality
